Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.36,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Found him! That's the guy!}Kìa! Tên đó đó!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.37,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Hurry!}Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.41,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\i1\be1}{Dammit, why do I have to \Ndo something like this...}Chết tiệt, tự nhiên vướng vào vụ này...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.88,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{H-Hold on...}K-Khoan...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.43,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{I wonder what this is!}Cái gì đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.43,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Hey, what are you doing?}Này, làm gì đó?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.68,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Photographs of a female student \Nattending this school?}Ảnh nữ sinh trường này à?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.27,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{She's rather pretty.}Xinh quá đi chứ.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.27,0:09:48.02,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Next up... well... a girl in her lingerie.}Tiếp theo... xem nào...\N chụp cả bộ đồ lót à...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.65,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{So this is thoughtography?\NYou sure use it for something stupid.}{Vậy ra đây là thấu thị?! Dùng để làm trò nhảm nhí thật.}Ra đây là niệm tả? \NĐúng là dùng năng lực vào mấy trò nhảm nhí.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.36,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Did you take these pictures?}Những bức ảnh này là cậu chụp à?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.07,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{N-No, I bought them...}K-Không, mua lại thôi...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.78,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Who did you buy them from?}Thế mua của ai?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.24,0:10:06.79,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{I don't intend of leaking any of this to a third party.\NPlease tell me just the truth.}Tôi sẽ không nói lại cho ai biết đâu. \NLàm ơn khai thật giùm đi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.79,0:10:12.80,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{If you don't tell us, I'll tell the girl in this photograph\Nthat this was in your possession..}Không chịu khai thì bọn tôi mách với \Ncô ta là cậu đang giữ mấy tấm hình này đó.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.80,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Udoh... in class 2-E.}Udou... lớp 2-E.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.76,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Thank you very much.}Cảm ơn nhiều nhé.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.97,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{We're going in!}Xông lên nào!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.10,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{We're out to capture Udoh from 2-E!}Tóm cổ Udou lớp 2-E!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.31,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Okay!}Rõ!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.31,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Has Udoh gone home yet?}Udou-san về chưa vậy?
