Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.89,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{If you don't want this photo \Ndistributed everywhere,}Nếu không muốn nó bị phát tán ra ngoài,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.23,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\Npretend like none of this ever happened!\be1}thì hãy xem như chưa có chuyện gì xảy ra đi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.27,0:11:52.27,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{That's all you have to do for a thoughtography?\NThat sure is something!}Chỉ cần làm vậy là có ảnh luôn sao? Lợi hại thật!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.94,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{But, nobody would ever \Nneed something like that.}Nhưng mà chả ai muốn ngắm nó đâu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.32,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{No matter who looks at you, \Nyou're an attractive one.}Nhìn thế nào cũng thấy cô xinh lắm mà.
