Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.67,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{The beef tongue bento box lunch\Nthat warms up when you pull a string!}Cơm hộp lưỡi bò ăn nhanh ấm bụng.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.13,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Isn't this just amazing?}Đã ghê chưa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.05,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\be1}{Yeah, I know about that.}Ừ, biết rồi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.72,Default,KeyVN,0,0,0,,{\i1\be1}{I didn't think it would \Nbe an express train...}Ai ngờ lại đi tàu tốc hành...
